    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Friedman writes: ''We don't just need the first black president. We need the first green president. We don't just need the first woman president. We need the first environmental president . . . a president who is tough enough to level with the American people about the profound economic, geopolitical and climate threats posed by our addiction to oil -- and to offer a real plan to reduce our dependence on fossil fuels.'' Hey, he is talking about Al Gore!</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>Friedman writes: ''We don't just need the first black president. We need the first green president. We don't just need the first woman president. We need the first environmental president . . . a president who is tough enough to level with the American people about the profound economic, geopolitical and climate threats posed by our addiction to oil -- and to offer a real plan to reduce our dependence on fossil fuels.'' Hey, he is talking about Al Gore!</p>
        <p>Donna Handy  Santa Barbara, Calif.</p>
      </block>
